{"tid":277151,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【狙擊風暴】渾水預告很快再向敏華發炮 (18:17)","createTime":"2017-06-09T11:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T13:49:52.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bbaf3e1bc7a5c963db92111a5eb22680a3317a64","tid":277151,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:10:42.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=CMWTgCHRgeOI9SoRx%2FQidv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=11d20b57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】內地傳媒報道，渾水創辦人Carson Block在敏華(01999)發表了澄清公告後，表示很快會做出有針對性的回覆，放出更多敏華造假的證據。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指出，有基金於敏華股價處於7港元以上加了淡倉，並透露好多人都搶着在7元以上加淡倉。基金透露，目前市場上對敏華的沽空未平倉量應超過1億股。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170609/20170609181729fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170609%2F20170609181729fi.html&d=CMWTgCHRgeOI9SoRx%2FQidv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=d110dad2\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170609/20170609181729fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"02b1ca8bdd504ffaabd7cf3b9f202d2c7b18e164","tid":277151,"uid":117786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T13:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}